			<p class="m-0 text-muted">I have always enjoyed building and designing random projects. I love exploring new technologies, solving problems, and creating systems of technologies that interact with each other. My projects can be fully software or bodjing physical components to create something new. I have found an interest in the amusement industry and especially with the roller coasters that influences my work. I find interest in their history, engineering design decisions, and the programming.</p>
			<p class="m-0 text-muted">Hello</p>
		</div>
	</section>
